287
00:15:22,106 --> 00:15:23,471
Acting rule number eight,

288
00:15:23,574 --> 00:15:25,371
don't be afraid to get physical.

289
00:15:26,944 --> 00:15:27,911
Ow!

290
00:15:28,045 --> 00:15:29,842
You know damn well
what I'm talking about!

291
00:15:29,947 --> 00:15:31,278
No, I don't!

292
00:15:31,983 --> 00:15:36,784
