I'll hear you say it, scoundrel!

293
00:15:37,789 --> 00:15:41,122
- Mom, can you give us a sec?
- Okay.

294
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:44,954
- There's chocolate and butterscotch.
- Okay, thanks. Now just...

295
00:15:45,062 --> 00:15:47,759
There are various kinds
of sprinkles and marshmallows.

296
00:15:47,866 --> 00:15:48,833
Just...

297
00:15:50,302 --> 00:15:52,395
Have you lost your mind?

298
00:15:52,938 --> 00:15:55,338
You were amazing!

299
00:15:55,441 --> 00:15:58,069
You completely just became
that character.

300
00:15:58,177 --> 00:16:00,077
Honestly, I wasn't so much playing Ted

301
00:16:00,179 --> 00:16:02,875
as I was just trying
to get out of Ted's way.

302
00:16:03,081 --> 00:16:04,605
What is wrong with you people?

303
00:16:04,716 --> 00:16:07,446
