because I was the runt of the family.

308
00:16:19,932 --> 00:16:22,765
For crying out loud, I'm only 6'4"!

309
00:16:25,804 --> 00:16:27,294
How good was my crying?

310
00:16:27,406 --> 00:16:29,169
You nailed it. See?

311
00:16:29,274 --> 00:16:32,641
Even at a gig you hate,
you still managed to love what you do.

312
00:16:33,812 --> 00:16:36,007
