for you at your new job.

313
00:16:36,615 --> 00:16:38,845
- You think so?
- I know so.

314
00:16:39,551 --> 00:16:40,711
Thanks, Grant.

315
00:16:41,119 --> 00:16:43,485
You're pretty smart, you know that?

316
00:16:47,259 --> 00:16:49,784
