that I hired to pretend to be my family.

328
00:17:33,406 --> 00:17:34,464
What?

329
00:17:34,807 --> 00:17:37,469
I just wanted you to think I had the life

330
00:17:37,577 --> 00:17:40,740
you wanted for me.
I wanted you to be proud of me.

331
00:17:41,548 --> 00:17:44,176
I know it sounds crazy,
and I am so sorry, Mom.

332
00:17:44,751 --> 00:17:48,118
- So Betty is not your wife?
- No.

333
00:17:48,821 --> 00:17:52,689
Thank God! I do not like that woman.

334
00:17:53,626 --> 00:17:55,423
- Really?
- Yes.

335
00:17:55,995 --> 00:17:57,587
And Tyler...

336
00:17:58,331 --> 00:18:01,562
I know I'm his grandma
and I'm supposed to love him,

337
00:18:01,668 --> 00:18:04,728
but I hate that kid. "Tyler no likey. "

338
00:18:04,837 --> 00:18:06,464
- What the hell is that?
- Right?

339
00:18:06,573 --> 00:18:10,806
