340
00:18:11,879 --> 00:18:13,904
I know! Aren't they horrible?

341
00:18:15,082 --> 00:18:16,982
So really, really, you're not mad?

342
00:18:17,618 --> 00:18:21,179
No, I'm just confused. I don't know
why you thought you had to do this.

343
00:18:21,655 --> 00:18:24,453
Barney, I love you,
perfect family or no perfect family.

344
00:18:24,558 --> 00:18:26,355
I love you no matter what.

345
00:18:27,194 --> 00:18:29,025
- Really?
- Really.

346
00:18:34,702 --> 00:18:37,136
Oh, I am so relieved

347
00:18:37,237 --> 00:18:40,638
because the truth is
I am as far from married

348
00:18:40,741 --> 00:18:42,732
