349
00:18:42,843 --> 00:18:46,108
My history with women
would shock and appall you.

350
00:18:46,213 --> 00:18:47,874
Doesn't matter. I still love you.

351
00:18:47,982 --> 00:18:50,849
Seriously, you can't imagine
the things I have done.

352
00:18:50,951 --> 00:18:53,545
Barney, when you were three,
I left you with a babysitter

353
00:18:53,654 --> 00:18:56,214
and spent three weeks
with Grand Funk Railroad,

354
00:18:56,323 --> 00:18:58,757
being passed around like a bong.

355
00:18:58,859 --> 00:19:00,053
Mommy!

356
00:19:01,095 --> 00:19:04,792
Just do me a favor.
If you ever do meet someone special,

357
00:19:04,898 --> 00:19:07,366
