358
00:19:07,801 --> 00:19:09,701
Take a shot at it, will you?

359
00:19:10,204 --> 00:19:12,764
Hey, Barney, cab's here.

360
00:19:16,276 --> 00:19:17,505
I'll try.

361
00:19:18,613 --> 00:19:22,310
<i>And so ended one of
the strangest afternoons of our lives.</i>

362
00:19:23,451 --> 00:19:25,715
And I just wanted to say to you,

363
00:19:25,820 --> 00:19:30,917
if I ever seemed cold
or unwelcoming, I'm sorry.

364
00:19:31,259 --> 00:19:33,454
- Who's she talking to?
- My mom.

365
00:19:34,095 --> 00:19:38,054
